{"tid":778230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"濱崎步高衩白裙開到大腿根 五官再進化引熱議","createTime":"2018-08-13T14:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T08:49:05.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"51efe8870e35d09f5d8c550cfca61f2292bed068","tid":778230,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"日本天后濱崎步「步姐」出道20周年，下禮拜將推出睽違2年多的新專輯《TROUBLE》，為紀念20周年大日子，11日她上節目《MUSIC FAIR》宣傳，大談出道20年的心路歷程，外貌和身材再次成為網友討論焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-12/656/20180812001738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-12%2F656%2F20180812001738.jpg&h=9001aa0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n濱崎步近年人氣大不如前，加上頻被指變臉、暴肥，即將推出的新專輯《TROUBLE》，封面和宣傳廣告也被指抄襲安室奈美惠，此子和摩連奴矛盾未解決，更衣室風波隨時拖累紅魔今季成績。11日她照樣上節目宣傳，大談出道後的心路歷程，並重溫過往演出片段，她表示20年來對自己音樂定位從來沒有變，也在現場演唱名曲《TO BE》、《Voyage》及新歌《&aelig;ternal》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-12/656/20180812001741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-12%2F656%2F20180812001741.jpg&h=eb2fdcec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而穿著一襲白色露肩長洋裝的她，旁邊開高衩到大腿根，坐下後裙子撩開，長腿全看光，豐滿上圍也相當搶鏡，但不斷進化的五官，依舊相當引人注意，成為網友討論焦點。"},{"pid":"ce924ab0f326e08e1a031c805d95098dd192fd03","tid":778230,"uid":48858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"摩佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4841cbf0d4b7e1c29e06bb77a66d09af2d6d7a30","tid":778230,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"日本女藝人最引以為傲就係純天然<br />\n宜家個個都整都無曬以前果種味道<br />\n諗番吉田禮同大塚愛果種pure真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2660ce73273ad78ff7b319b73ee4c2c4bd1c66a5","tid":778230,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTi